com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.regions

Class ServiceAbbreviations

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.regions.ServiceAbbreviations
  • Deprecated. 
    use the constant ENDPOINT_PREFIX from the specific service client interface instead for retrieving the specific service abbreviation, e.g. AmazonEC2.ENDPOINT_PREFIX.

    @Deprecated
public final class ServiceAbbreviations
extends Object
    Abbreviations for looking up information about a specific service. Used in Region.getServiceEndpoint(String) and related methods.
